@using ExploreJordan.Settings;
@using System.Security.Claims

@model ExploreJordan.ViewModels.CombinedViewModel
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<link href="~/csspop/ajloun.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Ajloun</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="Popular">
        <h2 style="text-align: center;margin-top:125px;">Ajloun</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="style-0">
        <div class="style-1">
            <div class="style-2">
                <div class="style-3" data-ft="true">
                    <div class="style-4">
                        <div class="style-5">
                            <button aria-label="See all photos" class="style-6">
                                <picture class="style-7">
                                    <img src="~/img2/ajloun/1.jpg" width="720" height="480" role="none" alt="" fetchpriority="high" class="style-11" />
                                </picture>
                            </button><button aria-label="See all photos" class="style-12">
                                <picture class="style-13">
                                    <img src="~/img2/ajloun/2.jpg" width="720" height="480" role="none" alt="" fetchpriority="high" class="style-17" />
                                </picture>
                            </button><button aria-label="See all photos" class="style-18">
                                <picture class="style-19">
                                    <img src="~/img2/ajloun/3.jpg" width="720" height="480" role="none" alt="" fetchpriority="high" class="style-23" />

                                </picture>
                            </button>
                            <p>About</p>
                            <p>Ajloun, nestled in the highlands of northern Jordan, is a captivating town offering a unique blend of historical charm, natural splendor, and cultural richness. Let's delve into its captivating story:<p>History:</p><p>Castle of Ajloun: Dominating the town, this 12th-century masterpiece built by Saladin stands as a testament to medieval Islamic military architecture.Ancient heritage: Archaeological discoveries reveal settlements dating back to the Neolithic period, showcasing Ajloun's long and vibrant history.Ottoman influence: Ajloun bears the mark of centuries of Ottoman rule, evident in its traditional architecture, mosques, and cultural traditions.</p>
                            <p>Nature:</p><p>Ajloun Forest Reserve: Lush and diverse, this enchanting reserve boasts a treasure trove of flora and fauna, offering scenic hiking trails and breathtaking views.Mountainous landscapes: Ajloun's hilly terrain provides magnificent panoramas, with valleys adorned by olive groves and orchards, offering a haven for nature lovers.Diverse ecosystems: From the rugged mountains to fertile valleys, Ajloun boasts a variety of ecosystems, each with its unique charm and ecological significance.</p>
                            </p>

                        </div>
                        <div class="style-27"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="style-28">
                <div class="style-29">
                    <section class="style-30">
                        <div data-automation="WebPresentation_ProductAboveTheFoldInfo" class="style-31">
                            <div class="style-32" data-ft="true">
                                <div class="style-33">
                                    <div class="style-34">
                                        <div class="style-35">
                                            <div class="style-36">About</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="style-37">
                                        <div class="style-38">
                                            <div class="style-39">
                                                <div class="style-40">
                                                    <p>Ajloun, nestled in the highlands of northern Jordan, is a captivating town offering a unique blend of historical charm, natural splendor, and cultural richness. Let's delve into its captivating story:<p>History:</p><p>Castle of Ajloun: Dominating the town, this 12th-century masterpiece built by Saladin stands as a testament to medieval Islamic military architecture.Ancient heritage: Archaeological discoveries reveal settlements dating back to the Neolithic period, showcasing Ajloun's long and vibrant history.Ottoman influence: Ajloun bears the mark of centuries of Ottoman rule, evident in its traditional architecture, mosques, and cultural traditions.</p>
                                                    <p>Nature:</p><p>Ajloun Forest Reserve: Lush and diverse, this enchanting reserve boasts a treasure trove of flora and fauna, offering scenic hiking trails and breathtaking views.Mountainous landscapes: Ajloun's hilly terrain provides magnificent panoramas, with valleys adorned by olive groves and orchards, offering a haven for nature lovers.Diverse ecosystems: From the rugged mountains to fertile valleys, Ajloun boasts a variety of ecosystems, each with its unique charm and ecological significance.</p>
                                                    </p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <section class="style-41">
                        <div data-automation="WebPresentation_ProductAboveTheFoldCommerce" class="style-42">
                            <div class="style-43" data-ft="true"></div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <section class="style-444">
                        <div data-automation="WebPresentation_ProductKeyDetailsSectionV2" class="style-45">
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="conwrap">
        @if (Model != null)
        {
            @if (Model.Activities != null)
            {
                @foreach (var activity in Model.Activities)
                {
                    if (activity.City != null && activity.City.Trim().Equals("Ajloun", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
                    {
                        <div class="CarRentalContainer0">
                            <div class="style-00">
                                <div class="style-01">
                                    <div class="style-02">
                                        <div class="style-03">
                                            <div class="style-05">
                                                <span class="style-06">
                                                    <span class="style-07">@activity.Name</span>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="imagesize0">
                                            <img src="@($"{FileSettings.ImagesPath}/{activity.Cover}")" alt="Car Image" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-09">
                                            <div>@activity.Description</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-052">

                                            <span class="style-053">
                                                <span class="style-054">@activity.Price</span>
                                                <span class="style-055">JD</span>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-051">
                                            <div class="style-056" data-testid="rc-itinerary-cta-button">
                                                <div class="style-057">
                                                    <a asp-controller="Activities" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@activity.Id" class="style-058">
                                                        <div class="style-059">View Deal</div>
                                                    </a>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                }
            }

            @if (Model.Accommodations != null)
            {
                @foreach (var accommodation in Model.Accommodations)
                {
                    if (accommodation.City != null && accommodation.City.Trim().Equals("Ajloun", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
                    {
                        <div class="CarRentalContainer">
                            <div class="style-00">
                                <div class="style-01">
                                    <div class="style-02">
                                        <div class="style-03">
                                            <div class="style-05">
                                                <span class="style-06">
                                                    <span class="style-07">@accommodation.Name</span>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="imagesize0">
                                            <img src="@($"{FileSettings.ImagesPath}/{accommodation.Cover}")" alt="Car Image" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-09">
                                            <div>@accommodation.Description</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-052">

                                            <span class="style-053">
                                                <span class="style-054">@accommodation.Price</span>
                                                <span class="style-055">JD/Day</span>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-051">
                                            <div class="style-056" data-testid="rc-itinerary-cta-button">
                                                <div class="style-057">
                                                    <a asp-controller="Accommodation" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@accommodation.Id" class="style-058">
                                                        <div class="style-059">View Deal</div>
                                                    </a>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                }
            }

            @if (Model.Tours != null)
            {
                @foreach (var tour in Model.Tours)
                {
                    if (tour.City != null && tour.City.Trim().Equals("Ajloun", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
                    {
                        <div class="CarRentalContainer">
                            <div class="style-00">
                                <div class="style-01">
                                    <div class="style-02">
                                        <div class="style-03">
                                            <div class="style-05">
                                                <span class="style-06">
                                                    <span class="style-07">@tour.Name</span>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="imagesize0">
                                            <img src="@($"{FileSettings.ImagesPath}/{tour.Cover}")" alt="Car Image" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-09">
                                            <div>@tour.Description</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-052">

                                            <span class="style-053">
                                                <span class="style-054">@tour.Price</span>
                                                <span class="style-055">JD</span>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-051">
                                            <div class="style-056" data-testid="rc-itinerary-cta-button">
                                                <div class="style-057">
                                                    <a asp-controller="Tours" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@tour.Id" class="style-058">
                                                        <div class="style-059">View Deal</div>
                                                    </a>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                }
            }
        }

    </div>
</body>
</html>